# Placeholder — this file is NOT a usable certificate.
#
# Generate your own client CA before enabling mTLS; never ship or reuse someone
# else's. Whoever holds the CA private key can mint client certificates your
# gateway will accept, so this must be yours and yours alone.
#
#   scripts/gen-client-cert.sh          # see deploy/traefik/README.md
#
# Then place the resulting CA certificate here as:
#   deploy/traefik/dynamic/retinue-client-ca.crt
#
# That path is referenced by retinue-mtls.yml (caFiles) and is .gitignore'd, so
# your CA never lands in git.
-----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----
REPLACE-WITH-YOUR-OWN-CLIENT-CA-CERTIFICATE
-----END CERTIFICATE-----
